.SH NAME
export \- Export data as JSON or CSV
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> export
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Prompts for format (json/csv) and output path.
.TP
Default output directory is exports/.
.TP
JSON export includes metadata (goals, reading list); CSV export focuses on books.
